divs: Sighting DetailsA Fire Truck passed my House, and I looked out the Window. A quick glance up at the Clouds, I saw a glowing object, gliding across the tops of the clouds, but bright enough to shine through. It lasted about 20 seconds and it was gone. Couldn't of been Lightning. Looked like a Craft of some kind.
